title: Mid-size luxury vehicles : sales by model in the United States 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Sales in units on the Y-axis for 17 different Models for 2 groups 2019, and 2018 that are presented on the X-axis.
Out of all 2 groups, 2019 had the highest Sales in units in Model Tesla Model 3 and 2019 had the lowest Sales in units in Model Acura RLX.
Among all the Models, 2018 had the highest Sales in units 140317.0 in Model Tesla Model 3 and lowest value 1931.0 in Model Acura RLX.
There is a gap of 138386.0 between the highest and lowest Sales in units found for 2018 in Model Tesla Model 3 and Acura RLX.
min_summary: This grouped bar chart represents 17 different Models on X-axis for 2 groups 2019, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding Sales in units.
